    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为Esophaguy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有可拉伸脖子的老人！<br>在1–4人喉咙混战中伸展、咬合、摆动自己：合作、对抗与单人。在每个模式中推进，团聚你失散的亲族。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/1f486a33c3804f4e28b58a25c907e5e5.avif?t=1758732586\" width=1000 height=389 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合作模式（2–4人）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一起伸展、咬合、摆动，穿越野外环境并解谜，寻找激活你流散民族被遗忘的纪念碑的方法。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/4e23bf3e2e9d5d37ef7ff5772937a0ea.poster.avif?t=1758732586\" width=800 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/4e23bf3e2e9d5d37ef7ff5772937a0ea.webm?t=1758732586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/4e23bf3e2e9d5d37ef7ff5772937a0ea.mp4?t=1758732586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >迷你游戏模式（2–4人）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Esophaball、Spartagus和Gulletorax等你来战。团队运动、竞技场和技巧挑战中脖颈对决，看看谁拥有最强咽喉。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/4e6c0980972553082ab3697a51f643c5.poster.avif?t=1758732586\" width=800 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/4e6c0980972553082ab3697a51f643c5.webm?t=1758732586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/4e6c0980972553082ab3697a51f643c5.mp4?t=1758732586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事模式（1–4人）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在感人至深的旁白陪伴下，踏上神话之旅，理解过去、塑造未来。你能揭开脖子的真正奥秘吗？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/56f6dd58537b931ee13dbd7d25f76946.poster.avif?t=1758732586\" width=800 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/56f6dd58537b931ee13dbd7d25f76946.webm?t=1758732586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/56f6dd58537b931ee13dbd7d25f76946.mp4?t=1758732586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >受虐模式（1–4人）</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有地面。没有检查点。只有脖子。在地狱般的氛围中挑战极限，非常适合速通玩家。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/b65bf383616ce4e595c5c5bcb18dc51b.poster.avif?t=1758732586\" width=800 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/b65bf383616ce4e595c5c5bcb18dc51b.webm?t=1758732586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/b65bf383616ce4e595c5c5bcb18dc51b.mp4?t=1758732586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >中心世界进度</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每个模式中推进时，重建你民族的古老纪念碑，发现秘密并解锁失落长脖亲族的服饰。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/68a711288b5d9d267d1d7cb6ef9a62b9.poster.avif?t=1758732586\" width=800 height=188 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/68a711288b5d9d267d1d7cb6ef9a62b9.webm?t=1758732586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/68a711288b5d9d267d1d7cb6ef9a62b9.mp4?t=1758732586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >弹拨声与老人哼唱</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在独一无二的音效世界。首款专注于人类最古老乐器之一——口弦琴的视频游戏。体验融合世界多元传统与大胆实验的古老声音。基于档案资料重建的数百年传统，来自美国、奥地利、不列颠群岛、印度、挪威、吉尔吉斯斯坦和雅库特的经典弹拨声，每一次脖颈摆动都让你的耳朵愉悦。配合4000多个亲自录制的口腔音效，准备好让耳蜗被极致“挠痒”吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/39c62afe91be663736466fea46fb6c8c.poster.avif?t=1758732586\" width=800 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/39c62afe91be663736466fea46fb6c8c.webm?t=1758732586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164300/extras/39c62afe91be663736466fea46fb6c8c.mp4?t=1758732586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
